{"tid":1965374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★施永青：無話賺錢唔申請得  中原集團一定申請","createTime":"2020-04-09T12:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:16:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"50196512d9b2b6ba482017373175bd31bae6d7be","tid":1965374,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2610000/2614515/0904_1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2610000%2F2614515%2F0904_1_1024.jpg&h=cec17ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中原集團主席施永青回應指，政府推出的措施幫助全個社會，中原集團（中原、利嘉閣）<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大約7000員工，一定會申請資助。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問及中原地產首3個月有利潤仍然申請資助有否心理包袱，施永青直言：「政府無話過賺唔可以申請，如果賺唔可申請即變相懲罰做得好的公司。」他又強調，今年首季並不是旗下所有公司賺錢，而且無人能保證未來數月一定賺錢，所以會申請政府資助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2614515/%E3%80%90%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E3%80%91%E6%96%BD%E6%B0%B8%E9%9D%92%EF%BC%9A%E7%84%A1%E8%A9%B1%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E5%94%94%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%BE%97%20%C2%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2614515%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E9%259D%2592%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25BE%2597%2520%25C2%25A0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=df72b3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2614515/%E3%80%90%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E3%80%91%E6%96%BD%E6%B0%B8%E9%9D%92%EF%BC%9A%E7%84%A1%E8%A9%B1%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2%E5%94%94%E7%9